{"tid":852402,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"最撚憎人打尖","createTime":"2018-10-07T23:33:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T01:13:12.000Z","uid":200641,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f4140fb89eadc9e3f88ef3a80812b23b24737dec","tid":852402,"uid":200641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T23:33:58.000Z","msg":"朝早係巴士總站排隊上巴士<br />\n條隊排到水蛇春咁款<br />\n個個都排緊隊上車個陣<br />\n我見前面突然有個廢老企咗係條隊隔離<br />\n行過佢之後佢插咗黎我後面<br />\n我望一望後面 無人出聲 但個樣就閪口閪面<br />\n我咪停撚咗係到 擰轉身同個廢老講要排隊 隊尾係邊<br />\n個廢老一路話排緊 一路行後幾個插埋去<br />\n我後尾上車望返條隊 個廢老係成功上撚咗車<br />\n有啲仆街持老賣老 拎2蚊搭車 又唔係返工返學<br />\n死都要打尖 其實好撚唔公平 個個等咁耐 佢一入黎就上車<br />\n因為真係可以出聲 隊尾班人根本唔知隊頭有人打尖<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">或者我認真咗</span>"},{"pid":"5a6b106b41391fca3a276653b1cd33266a80c33b","tid":852402,"uid":203333,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T23:39:49.000Z","msg":"巴士都好啲 小巴就真係多撚謝佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時趕時間 差一個位又要等下班車"},{"pid":"8f8a689f96ac49f794d08bfa80ef7c9a2068c14a","tid":852402,"uid":200641,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5a6b106b41391fca3a276653b1cd33266a80c33b","tid":852402,"uid":203333,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T23:39:49.000Z","msg":"巴士都好啲 小巴就真係多撚謝佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時趕時間 差一個位又要等下班車"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T23:42:19.000Z","msg":"打尖都要死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05d74f7424d34af1927205e4327fbccddd3ad9f0","tid":852402,"uid":40087,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T23:52:17.000Z","msg":"香港人真係唔撚扺幫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有次去完旅行, 喺泡菜國機場排隊等 check in, 我同老婆排第一位埋咗 counter, 突然隔離有三條死支那學生走埋黎我地後面, 話排錯隊過返黎排, 其實唔關我事, 佢打我後面尖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我即場同佢地講<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> = 支那人<br />\n<br />\n我: 話之你之前排幾耐, 排錯隊就要重新排過架啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 關你L事咩咁多聲氣<br />\n我: 係唔關我事, 但你地打晒後面咁多人尖喎, 一係你地問吓我後面嗰個比唔比你地打尖囉<br />\n<br />\n 之後我望住後面個香港後生女同佢講 &ldquo;佢地打緊妳尖喎, 點解妳唔出句聲嘅?&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n仆佢個街, 條女同我講: &ldquo;算啦, 由佢地啦&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n我即場呆咗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仆街有人幫緊佢都可以咁怕事, 佢又無做錯, 明明自己嘅權益比侵蝕緊, 道理喺晒我地尼邊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以我決定以後都唔主動幫香港人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de05b3dc4eae44314ca17082756aeab14f89fb52","tid":852402,"uid":212760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T23:54:10.000Z","msg":"係到濫用人地嘅同情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8777bfccf8a4cb44ba8a9c3a7677dcba0d67c995","tid":852402,"uid":200641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"05d74f7424d34af1927205e4327fbccddd3ad9f0","tid":852402,"uid":40087,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T23:52:17.000Z","msg":"香港人真係唔撚扺幫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有次去完旅行, 喺泡菜國機場排隊等 check in, 我同老婆排第一位埋咗 counter, 突然隔離有三條死支那學生走埋黎我地後面, 話排錯隊過返黎排, 其實唔關我事, 佢打我後面尖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我即場同佢地講<br />\n<img src=\"/